{"tid":350244,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"印度拳手讓金腰帶予中國敗將：中印需要和平","createTime":"2017-08-07T05:56:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-08T15:56:02.000Z","uid":76115,"like":41,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"64b5559158fe4c1d673b04cd233cff07ca17d856","tid":350244,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T05:56:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://goo.gl/1v4Nfq\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2F1v4Nfq&d=IzYqItrksY8bkNbUn20PjZ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=439a55c9\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/1v4Nfq</a><br />\n<br />\n中印邊境對峙踏入第7個星期，而在印度孟買一個拳擊場上，中國和印度選手則是拳拳到肉，為爭奪金腰帶殊榮在台上鬥個你死我活。<br />\n然而發生了一件出人意表的插曲－－勝者「為了兩國友誼」，想將金腰帶退還。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/750793/xlarge/7b6d9a38b43d1fd2f3331c0d3d152fdc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F750793%2Fxlarge%2F7b6d9a38b43d1fd2f3331c0d3d152fdc.jpg&h=388ad8c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n印度拳擊手辛格（左）在比賽中打贏中國選手祖力皮卡爾（右），但他希望金腰帶獻給兩國友誼。（網上圖片）<br />\n<br />\n印度「國寶級」拳擊手辛格（Vijender Singh）在周六（5日）一場WBO東方金腰帶和亞太金腰帶的統一戰中，打敗中國選手祖力皮卡爾（Zulpikar Maimaitiali），獲得代表勝利的金腰帶。今年31歲的辛格是首名在奧運拳擊項目上的獲獎牌的選手，他現在同時獲得東方金腰帶和亞太金腰帶兩個勝者頭銜。<br />\n<br />\n但辛格表示，想將勝利獻予「印中關係」 ，又希望將勝者頭銜送給人民，和平和兩國友誼。「我不想要這個頭銜。我想把它給祖力皮卡爾。我想把這次勝利獻給印中友誼。（中印）邊境間出現磨擦，（而那裏）需要和平。」辛格勝出後說道。此前，辛格對此拳賽信心滿滿，<strong>更曾表示「中國製造的不能捱太久」（Chinese products don't last long）</strong>，意指對手祖力皮卡爾在賽事中將很快敗陣。"},{"pid":"ae864bb981f8b6f9961598ca0f631262f6d7693f","tid":350244,"uid":76115,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T05:57:20.000Z","msg":"好撚串<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90dc9df3fe8fc95682ea72fd70aaec2b3bec6600","tid":350244,"uid":52122,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T05:57:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好撚串<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n撚狗咁撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac252a6dd8790be1472b54bff61d33a0932e8967","tid":350244,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T05:58:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好撚串<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n撚狗咁撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n串9你係主題<br />\n中印關係只係借個名"},{"pid":"5149015d91bf490e65f8c0c88d2d26b4e29677af","tid":350244,"uid":112583,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T05:58:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">「中國製造的不能捱太久」（Chinese products don't last long）</span></span>"},{"pid":"8a4da2e5493ec5f02b0941eb71cc92d0248df3d5","tid":350244,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T06:00:49.000Z","msg":"腦海浮現出黃子華《修橋補路》<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7e30e6666f9bcbf47ac245ebf7e0470773025d5","tid":350244,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T06:02:03.000Z","msg":"咁樣hurt黃皮狗小心佢咬鳩你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e87c02d2c26d33d0ecfacbe2e0f1ebe95f077163","tid":350244,"uid":41205,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T06:05:44.000Z","msg":"咖哩仔大人有大量<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"921edb86f0d23a7d7d8ae05b41c337317746584e","tid":350244,"uid":21716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T06:07:08.000Z","msg":"上次鄒市明打輸俾個日本咕哩已經夠柒"},{"pid":"c62039091f018383cbe84c57f7df94187888d0db","tid":350244,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T06:07:17.000Z","msg":"大國國民氣度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2543030f204108449e23accb2d3c3d6c78bcf9e2","tid":350244,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T06:07:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>好撚串<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n撚狗咁撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n串9你係主題<br />\n中印關係只係借個名</blockquote><br />\n又攞彩又攞道德高地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adfbb009df84090e59633efeb4f9ca19431ded3e","tid":350244,"uid":61363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T06:08:03.000Z","msg":"中國選手叫祖力皮卡爾？"},{"pid":"5b4833dc2a7eac7dd16a209ad72c1e504209d55a","tid":350244,"uid":1139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T06:10:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9b156b5d7c6f9fa1d29deb013bcbc23dc8e9b7e4","tid":350244,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T06:11:26.000Z","msg":"串中國可以用一條腰帶收買到"},{"pid":"7dfb4bbd929978ba4b34b26a1219247b3391fde7","tid":350244,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T06:12:11.000Z","msg":"一條腰帶就想唔打....on 9"},{"pid":"2e328c9441d37e171b612b7c999ab9599c589f33","tid":350244,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T06:12:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/column/%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%83%B3%E6%89%93%EF%BC%8C%E5%8D%B0%E5%BA%A6%E4%B8%8D%E6%83%B3%E6%89%93-90022\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.am730.com.hk%2Fcolumn%2F%25E8%25B2%25A1%25E7%25B6%2593%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%2583%25B3%25E6%2589%2593%25EF%25BC%258C%25E5%258D%25B0%25E5%25BA%25A6%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%2583%25B3%25E6%2589%2593-90022&d=IzYqItrksY8bkNbUn20PjZ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=2071a2af\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/column/%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%83%B3%E6%89%93%EF%BC%8C%E5%8D%B0%E5%BA%A6%E4%B8%8D%E6%83%B3%E6%89%93-90022</a><br />\n<br />\n對外方面，印度野心勃勃，覬覦西藏、劍指巴基斯坦，向來是中國的敵人，經濟上也想和中國爭雄，近年發展的速度快過中國，也有西方和日本的支持，因此中國也不無誘因教訓一下印度，有助於穩定西方邊境的局勢，也是旁敲側擊了日本。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n那為何中國不動手呢？皆因中國爭取的是國際輿論的支持，所以不能開第一槍，因此只能大軍壓境，給印度不好受。換言之，現時中國的前線，是外交，優勢是它的目標並非侵略不丹，只是令到不丹不陷入印度之手而已。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n至於印度狀況十分尷尬：不丹是吃了很多年、含在口中的肥肉，不可能甩掉。但要正面和中國交鋒，又沒有勝算。如果撤兵，難看還是其次，而是印度地方主義嚴重，中央政府威權不足，好不容易出了一個強勢的莫迪，一旦給中國打臉，地方土豪又會乘機割據，東北部少數民族的分離主義更加會猖獗起來&hellip;&hellip;別忘記，9年前孟買才受過195人死亡、295人受傷的恐怖襲擊。結論是：中國正在等待戰爭的機會，印度則是騎虎難下。戰爭有利中國，前提當然是，戰事須如預期般獲勝，否則&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"7349a3a8f0fc7feff1c480c3d12fb23ca0094479","tid":350244,"uid":65346,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T06:14:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咖哩仔大人有大量<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n印度人出名小氣"},{"pid":"21c634cb37c94a3ffecc8dd43a2d9987b4d37d2a","tid":350244,"uid":41076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T06:17:08.000Z","msg":"印度佬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60cd353758f16ce1ca46573c787af55ef49bf350","tid":350244,"uid":33787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T06:18:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2c7f3be2b0e1ffed9247466ee83fd753897ca361","tid":350244,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T06:18:46.000Z","msg":"送兩條女俾佢強姦重實際"},{"pid":"525a8a744cdf0e160f1c86cc52ec30838872139d","tid":350244,"uid":82640,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T06:22:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咖哩仔大人有大量<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n印度人出名小氣</blockquote><br />\n1. 印度人出名小氣<br />\n2. 咖哩仔大人有大量<br />\n3. 印度人&lt;=&gt;咖哩仔<br />\n<br />\n中國人應該小器過方丈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eecaa1fc62b8dae311eb704fafab0f1f8100c2c3","tid":350244,"uid":33874,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T06:25:14.000Z","msg":"串到仆街，打贏仲要<br />\ni dun give a fuck，條腰帶你要咪要囉"},{"pid":"5cbb67ac99268a1ca10adfc1bfa6a6f491e831a6","tid":350244,"uid":17103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T06:27:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/column/%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%83%B3%E6%89%93%EF%BC%8C%E5%8D%B0%E5%BA%A6%E4%B8%8D%E6%83%B3%E6%89%93-90022\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.am730.com.hk%2Fcolumn%2F%25E8%25B2%25A1%25E7%25B6%2593%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%2583%25B3%25E6%2589%2593%25EF%25BC%258C%25E5%258D%25B0%25E5%25BA%25A6%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%2583%25B3%25E6%2589%2593-90022&d=IzYqItrksY8bkNbUn20PjZ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=2071a2af\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/column/%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%83%B3%E6%89%93%EF%BC%8C%E5%8D%B0%E5%BA%A6%E4%B8%8D%E6%83%B3%E6%89%93-90022</a><br />\n<br />\n對外方面，印度野心勃勃，覬覦西藏、劍指巴基斯坦，向來是中國的敵人，經濟上也想和中國爭雄，近年發展的速度快過中國，也有西方和日本的支持，因此中國也不無誘因教訓一下印度，有助於穩定西方邊境的局勢，也是旁敲側擊了日本。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n那為何中國不動手呢？皆因中國爭取的是國際輿論的支持，所以不能開第一槍，因此只能大軍壓境，給印度不好受。換言之，現時中國的前線，是外交，優勢是它的目標並非侵略不丹，只是令到不丹不陷入印度之手而已。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n至於印度狀況十分尷尬：不丹是吃了很多年、含在口中的肥肉，不可能甩掉。但要正面和中國交鋒，又沒有勝算。如果撤兵，難看還是其次，而是印度地方主義嚴重，中央政府威權不足，好不容易出了一個強勢的莫迪，一旦給中國打臉，地方土豪又會乘機割據，東北部少數民族的分離主義更加會猖獗起來&hellip;&hellip;別忘記，9年前孟買才受過195人死亡、295人受傷的恐怖襲擊。結論是：中國正在等待戰爭的機會，印度則是騎虎難下。戰爭有利中國，前提當然是，戰事須如預期般獲勝，<span style=\"color: red;\">否則</span>&hellip;&hellip;</blockquote>"},{"pid":"66f87a0af6dea50e33d2c1a3502975902eef5e7f","tid":350244,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T06:37:13.000Z","msg":"鍚克教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad7a25245c68494a16dbc60b3c925ccd2ad3f1f2","tid":350244,"uid":75694,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T06:45:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">「中國製造的不能捱太久」（Chinese products don't last long）</span></span></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> but still better than Indian products"}]}